---
import Base from '../layouts/base.astro';
import LegalText from '../components/blocks/LegalText.astro';

const body = `
<p class="text-[13px] text-ink-3">Version: 1.0-draft &middot; Last updated: 4 May 2026</p>

<p>
  This Data Processing Agreement ("DPA") supplements the
  <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> when Initlabs B.V. processes personal
  data on behalf of a Customer acting as a Controller under GDPR Article 28.
</p>

<h2>1. Parties</h2>
<p>
  <strong>Processor:</strong> Initlabs B.V., Kelvinstraat 34A, 6601 HE Wijchen,
  Netherlands (KvK 95157565) ("Beebeeb").<br />
  <strong>Controller:</strong> the legal entity that has accepted the Terms of
  Service and uses Beebeeb for business or professional purposes ("Customer").
</p>

<h2>2. Scope and nature of processing</h2>
<p>
  Beebeeb processes personal data on behalf of the Customer solely to provide
  the encrypted cloud storage service described in the Terms of Service. The
  nature of processing is storage, retrieval, and deletion of end-to-end
  encrypted file objects. Beebeeb cannot access the content of stored files
  (zero-knowledge architecture).
</p>

<h2>3. Categories of data subjects</h2>
<p>
  The Customer's end users, employees, or other individuals whose personal data
  may be included in files uploaded to Beebeeb. The actual content is
  encrypted and inaccessible to Beebeeb.
</p>

<h2>4. Duration</h2>
<p>
  This DPA is effective for the duration of the Customer's subscription and
  terminates automatically upon account deletion.
</p>

<h2>5. Processor obligations (GDPR Article 28)</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Process personal data only on documented instructions from the Customer (i.e., the service the Customer has subscribed to).</li>
  <li>Ensure personnel with access to personal data are bound by confidentiality.</li>
  <li>Implement appropriate technical and organisational measures (see Section 7).</li>
  <li>Engage sub-processors only under a written agreement with equivalent obligations. See our <a href="/sub-processors">sub-processor list</a>.</li>
  <li>Assist the Customer with data subject requests (access, erasure, portability) where technically feasible. Note: we cannot assist with access to encrypted file content as we do not hold the keys.</li>
  <li>Notify the Customer without undue delay (and within 72 hours where required) of any personal data breach.</li>
  <li>Delete or return personal data on termination, at the Customer's choice.</li>
  <li>Make available information necessary to demonstrate compliance.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Data location and transfers</h2>
<p>
  All personal data is processed within the European Economic Area (Hetzner
  Online GmbH, Germany and Finland). No personal data is transferred outside
  the EEA. If that changes, we will update this DPA and notify Customers 30 days
  in advance.
</p>

<h2>7. Technical and organisational measures</h2>
<ul>
  <li>End-to-end encryption: AES-256-GCM, keys derived client-side with HKDF-SHA256.</li>
  <li>Transport encryption: TLS 1.3 for all connections.</li>
  <li>Access control: role-based, with MFA for administrative access.</li>
  <li>Audit logging: tamper-evident hash-chained audit log for all administrative actions.</li>
  <li>Vulnerability management: bug bounty programme, see <a href="/bug-bounty">beebeeb.io/bug-bounty</a>.</li>
  <li>Data centre security: ISO 27001-certified facilities (Hetzner).</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Liability</h2>
<p>
  Each party is liable for damages caused by processing in infringement of GDPR
  as set out in GDPR Articles 82–83. Our liability under this DPA is limited
  as described in the Terms of Service.
</p>

<h2>9. Governing law</h2>
<p>
  This DPA is governed by Netherlands law.
</p>

<h2>10. Contact</h2>
<p>
  For DPA-related enquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@beebeeb.io">hello@beebeeb.io</a>
</p>
`;
---

<Base
  title="Data Processing Agreement — Beebeeb"
  description="Beebeeb DPA for business customers. GDPR Article 28 data processing agreement."
  path="/dpa"
>
  <!-- Draft banner -->
  <div class="bg-amber-bg border-b border-amber/40 px-8 py-3 text-center text-[13px]" style="color: var(--color-amber-deep);">
    <strong>DRAFT</strong> — Under legal review. Not yet in effect. For executed DPAs, contact <a href="mailto:hello@beebeeb.io" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;">hello@beebeeb.io</a>.
  </div>

  <LegalText title="Data Processing Agreement" body={body} />
</Base>
